import sys
input = iter(sys.stdin.read().splitlines()).__next__

def solve(S):
    numN = len([c for c in S if c == 'N'])
    return numN != 1
TC = int(input())
for tc in range(TC):
    S = input()
    res = solve(S)
    print('YES' if res else 'NO')
